---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import logoImage from '../assets/logo.png';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="홈"
  description="YumYum 맛집 다이어리 앱의 공식 지원 사이트입니다. 나만의 맛집 기록 앱 다운로드, 사용법, FAQ 등의 정보를 확인하세요."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-50 to-pink-50 py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="flex justify-center mb-8">
          <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-white rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
            <img 
              src={logoImage.src} 
              alt="YumYum 로고" 
              class="w-full h-full object-contain"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
          <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-400 to-pink-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
            YumYum
          </span>
        </h1>
        
        <p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl text-gray-700 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          나만의 맛집 다이어리, 지금 시작하세요<br />
          <span class="text-gray-600">내가 직접 찾은 맛집을 손쉽게 기록하고 관리하는 개인 맛집 노트</span>
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center">
          <a 
            href="#" 
            class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-black text-white rounded-xl font-medium hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors shadow-lg"
          >
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 mr-3" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M18.71 19.5c-.83 1.24-1.71 2.45-3.05 2.47-1.34.03-1.77-.79-3.29-.79-1.53 0-2 .77-3.27.82-1.31.05-2.3-1.32-3.14-2.53C4.25 17 2.94 12.45 4.7 9.39c.87-1.52 2.43-2.48 4.12-2.51 1.28-.02 2.5.87 3.29.87.78 0 2.26-1.07 3.81-.91.65.03 2.47.26 3.64 1.98-.09.06-2.17 1.28-2.15 3.81.03 3.02 2.65 4.03 2.68 4.04-.03.07-.42 1.44-1.38 2.83M13 3.5c.73-.83 1.94-1.46 2.94-1.5.13 1.17-.34 2.35-1.04 3.19-.69.85-1.83 1.51-2.95 1.42-.15-1.15.41-2.35 1.05-3.11z"/>
            </svg>
            App Store에서 다운로드
          </a>
          
          <a 
            href="#" 
            class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-green-600 text-white rounded-xl font-medium hover:bg-green-700 transition-colors shadow-lg"
          >
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 mr-3" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M3,20.5V3.5C3,2.91 3.34,2.39 3.84,2.15L13.69,12L3.84,21.85C3.34,21.61 3,21.09 3,20.5M16.81,15.12L6.05,21.34L14.54,12.85L16.81,15.12M20.16,10.81C20.5,11.08 20.75,11.5 20.75,12C20.75,12.5 20.53,12.9 20.18,13.18L17.89,14.5L15.39,12L17.89,9.5L20.16,10.81M6.05,2.66L16.81,8.88L14.54,11.15L6.05,2.66Z"/>
            </svg>
            Google Play에서 다운로드
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Features Section -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
          YumYum의 주요 기능
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          위치, 방문 날짜, 평점, 사진, 메모까지 한눈에 정리하여 나만의 맛집 노트를 만들어보세요
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Feature 1: 위치 기반 등록 -->
        <div class="text-center p-6 rounded-xl hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-orange-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-orange-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">위치 기반 등록</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            지도에서 원하는 위치를 꾹 누르면 핀이 생성되고, + 버튼으로 맛집을 쉽게 등록할 수 있습니다
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Feature 2: 사진과 메모 기록 -->
        <div class="text-center p-6 rounded-xl hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-pink-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-pink-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 9a2 2 0 012-2h.93a2 2 0 001.664-.89l.812-1.22A2 2 0 0110.07 4h3.86a2 2 0 011.664.89l.812 1.22A2 2 0 0018.07 7H19a2 2 0 012 2v9a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V9z" />
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 13a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">사진과 메모 기록</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            방문 당시의 맛과 분위기를 사진과 메모로 생생하게 남겨 소중한 순간을 간직하세요
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Feature 3: 평점 및 마커 선택 -->
        <div class="text-center p-6 rounded-xl hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.519 4.674a1 1 0 00.95.69h4.915c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-3.976 2.888a1 1 0 00-.363 1.118l1.518 4.674c.3.922-.755 1.688-1.538 1.118l-3.976-2.888a1 1 0 00-1.176 0l-3.976 2.888c-.783.57-1.838-.197-1.538-1.118l1.518-4.674a1 1 0 00-.363-1.118l-3.976-2.888c-.784-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h4.914a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.519-4.674z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">평점 및 마커 선택</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            별점과 감정 마커로 나의 취향에 따라 맛집을 분류하고 관리할 수 있습니다
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 4: 즐겨찾기 기능 -->
        <div class="text-center p-6 rounded-xl hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-green-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">즐겨찾기 기능</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            자주 찾는 맛집을 별표로 표시하여 별도로 모아 빠르게 확인할 수 있습니다
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 5: 캘린더 연동 -->
        <div class="text-center p-6 rounded-xl hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-purple-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">캘린더 연동</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            저장한 맛집 방문 일정을 캘린더에서 바로 확인하고 관리할 수 있습니다
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 6: 다크 모드 지원 -->
        <div class="text-center p-6 rounded-xl hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gray-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-gray-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M20.354 15.354A9 9 0 018.646 3.646 9.003 9.003 0 0012 21a9.003 9.003 0 008.354-5.646z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">다크 모드 지원</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            상황에 맞게 밝기와 분위기를 전환하여 언제든 편안하게 앱을 사용할 수 있습니다
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Usage Guide Section -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
          YumYum 사용 가이드
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          간단한 몇 단계로 나만의 맛집 다이어리를 시작해보세요
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <!-- Left: Usage Steps -->
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-orange-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg">
              1
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">맛집 등록하기</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">지도 화면에서 원하는 위치를 꾹 누르면 핀이 생성됩니다. 화면 오른쪽 + 버튼을 눌러 맛집을 등록하세요.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-pink-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg">
              2
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">상세 정보 입력</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">방문 날짜, 제목, 내용, 마커, 평점, 사진 등을 등록하여 맛집에 대한 자세한 기록을 남겨보세요.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg">
              3
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">맛집 관리하기</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">저장한 맛집은 피드와 캘린더에서 확인 가능하며, 즐겨찾기로 설정하여 빠르게 접근할 수 있습니다.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-green-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg">
              4
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">편집 및 검색</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">피드에서 맛집 정보를 수정하거나, 검색 기능으로 등록된 맛집을 이름으로 빠르게 찾을 수 있습니다.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Right: Key Features Highlight -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 text-center">핵심 기능</h3>
          
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-orange-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-orange-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-gray-700">지도 기반 위치 등록</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-pink-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-pink-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-gray-700">사진 및 메모 첨부</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-gray-700">별점 및 감정 마커</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-gray-700">즐겨찾기 관리</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-purple-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-purple-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-gray-700">캘린더 연동</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-gray-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gray-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-gray-700">다크 모드 지원</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="mt-8 text-center">
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 italic">
              "소중한 순간이 모여, 나만의 맛집 지도가 완성됩니다."
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-400 to-pink-500">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
        특별한 식사 경험을 간직하세요
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-orange-100 mb-8">
        나만의 맛집 다이어리를 지금 바로 시작하고, 소중한 순간들을 기록해보세요
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a 
          href="#" 
          class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-white text-gray-900 rounded-xl font-medium hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors shadow-lg"
        >
          지금 다운로드하기
        </a>
        <a 
          href={import.meta.env.BASE_URL + "/faq/"} 
          class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 border-2 border-white text-white rounded-xl font-medium hover:bg-white hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors"
        >
          더 알아보기
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>